comment: Minha pele tá bem melhor, depois de eu começar a fazer as dicas da nossa amiga coreana

These are great tips, great video! But I would avoid puckering your lips like this 7:58 because it creates wrinkles on the upper lip, it's the same as drinking from a straw or smoking, or eating with your mouth full, all these habits create lots of wrinkles later. Mature people usually stress how the wrinkles above the top lip are really difficult to get rid of, almost impossible, and even I'm 38 and I begin to see them.
